Join us in welcoming our newest Alikay™ Ambassador, the stunning @it_is_alanna! Alanna is a vital addition to the Alikay Naturals™ family, playing a key role in helping us reconnect with our customers through her genuine influence.

Just take a moment to appreciate her beauty! Alanna’s hair is a gorgeous blend of kinky and curly textures, and we’re certain that many of you can pick up some  valuable haircare tips from her.

Beyond her fabulous texture, Alanna is a model, a double graduate from MSU, and a resident of MEM | STK | CLE 📍. Now, she proudly holds the title of #alikayambassador, and she’s extending the love with a special code, ALANNA15, for 15% off your order.

A warm welcome to Alanna, the newest member of our team! 🌿🌟💖
